data.title: Guess who's hooking up again? Ryan Phillippe and Australian…
data.meta_description: Guess who's hooking up again? Ryan Phillippe and Australian actress Abbie Cornish get cozy at a friends house in Beverly Hills, CA on Tuesday. Cornish famously had an affair with Phillippe that ended his 7 year marriage to actress Reese Witherspoon. Check out that ring on Abbie’s ring finger. Is it…
